# Canonical author identities (Group 8).
# Maps the names/emails used in commits to those used in the report and the
# contribution tracker, so `git shortlog -sne` and `git log` attribute every
# commit to the right member. In particular, Serein's commits were authored
# under her GitHub noreply address; this maps them to her ALU email.
